OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FUS envoys are expected to travel to
OL,7,FPakistan over the weekend in a renewed
OL,8,Fattempt to salvage ceasefire talks
OL,9,Fwith Tehran, but Iran has ruled out
OL,10,Fdirect negotiations with US officials.
OL,12,FThe latest effort to broker a deal
OL,13,Fcomes as an indefinite ceasefire has
OL,14,Fpaused most fighting, but the economic
OL,15,Fimpacts are being widely felt with
OL,16,Fglobal energy shipments disrupted by
OL,17,Fthe closure of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
