OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777179877
OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FThe White House said President Donald
OL,7,FTrump is sending Steve Witkoff and
OL,8,FJared Kushner to meet with Iran's
OL,9,FForeign Minister Abbas Araghchi.
OL,11,FShortly after Araghchi arrived in
OL,12,FIslamabad, his ministry said any talks
OL,13,Fwould be indirect, with messages
OL,14,Fconveyed between the two sides by
OL,15,FPakistani officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
