PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777179877
OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FAraghchi and the two Trump envoys held
OL,7,Fhours of indirect talks in Geneva on
OL,8,FFebruary 27 over Tehran's nuclear
OL,9,Fprogramme, but walked away without a
OL,10,Fdeal. The next day, Israel and the
OL,11,FUnited States started the war against
OL,12,FIran.
OL,14,FWhite House press secretary Karoline
OL,15,FLeavitt told Fox News that the
OL,16,Fpresident had decided to send Witkoff
OL,17,Fand Kushner to Pakistan "to hear the
OL,18,FIranians out."
OL,26,@yD@YOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
