OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"We've certainly seen some progress
OL,12,Ffrom the Iranian side in the last
OL,13,Fcouple of days," Leavitt said. She did
OL,14,Fnot offer any details about what US
OL,15,Fofficials were hearing.
OL,17,FEurope should "get in a boat", Hegseth
OL,18,Fsays
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
