PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777179877
OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FOn Friday US War Secretary Pete
OL,7,FHegseth called on Europe to end its
OL,8,F"fancy conferences" about the Strait
OL,9,Fof Hormuz and "get in a boat", as he
OL,10,Fonce again criticised the lack of
OL,11,Fsupport for the American war in Iran.
OL,13,F"We are not counting on Europe, but
OL,14,Fthey need the Strait of Hormuz much
OL,15,Fmore than we do, and they might want
OL,16,Fto start doing less talking and having
OL,17,Fless fancy conferences in Europe and
OL,18,Fget in a boat," Hegseth said.
OL,20,F"This is much more their fight than
OL,21,Fours."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777179877
OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FHegseth went on to say he had seen a
OL,7,F"silly conference in Europe last week"
OL,8,Fwhere he described attendees as
OL,9,F"talking about talking and maybe doing
OL,10,Fsomething eventually when things are
OL,11,Fdone".
OL,13,FHe said the US would welcome "serious"
OL,14,FEuropean efforts, noting that the
OL,15,Fcontinent has suffered more than his
OL,16,Fown nation because the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz has been closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
