OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777179877
OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,F"It's a wake-up call for countries
OL,7,Faround the world. Either you have
OL,8,Fcapabilities, or you don't," Hegseth
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FTensions linger in Lebanon despite
OL,12,Fceasefire
OL,14,FThe situation in Lebanon remained
OL,15,Ftense after Trump on Thursday
OL,16,Fannounced that Israel and Lebanon had
OL,17,Fagreed to extend a ceasefire between
OL,18,FIsrael and Hezbollah by three weeks.
OL,20,FHezbollah has not participated in the
OL,21,Fsituation brokered by Washington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
