OL,3,CTrump sends envoys to Pakistan as Iran
OL,4,Crules out direct talks
OL,6,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu, in a video statement
OL,8,Freleased by his office on Friday,
OL,9,Fhailed "a process to achieve a
OL,10,Fhistoric peace between Israel and
OL,11,FLebanon".
OL,13,FEarlier, the Israeli army asked
OL,14,Fresidents of the southern Lebanese
OL,15,Fvillage of Deir Aames to evacuate,
OL,16,Fsaying Hezbollah was using the village
OL,17,Fto launch attacks against Israel.
